title: BEST Lower Abs & Booty INTENSE Fat Burning TABATA | Abs & Booty Workout Challenge
description:
40 MIN TABATA?!?!? "ABSURD!" They said...

This workout will TEST you, but i know for a fact that you can do it. IF at any point in this workout, you feel a little overworked or overwhelmed, take a break sis...its okay, it really is. There is no need to overdo it - the results will come if you stay consistent and keep slowly chipping away at your goal. If you do this, your results will be more permanent and sustainable!

Todays’ workout starts with a 5 minute warm up - we will be doing 1 minute for each exercise.

Then we will go into the tabata portion of the workout (the remaining 35 mins). We will be doing each exercise twice. The first round will be a “practice round” and the second we are going to go ALL OUT! You heard me sis, ALL OUT

Lower Belly and Booty TABATA 
Apple Watch Setting: Indoor Walk/Mixed Cardio
Intensity: 10/10
Calories Burned: 515
Length: 40 mins

If any of the exercises are too challenging for you or youre just not feeling the vibe, just walk it out. Our main goal is to keep our heart rate up, complete the workout, and to get that amazing afterburn!!
